name: C for Cool & Creative
description:
We are cool and creative. We cherish all this in us because when we were growing up these qualities were not much valued.

Kidult Alphabet by Kato Trofimova

The Kidult Alphabet is my fun attempt to speak about my generation. We grew up in the 90s, with a Tetris in our hands. We raised a flock of tamagotchis and learned a million ways on how to blow a bubble from Love Is cherry gum. What I want to say is that even though we are grown-ups, we will always be kids, and this is totally dope!
